│ $ bin/opt -p loop-vectorize -S --debug-only= /tmp/reprod_mij23t7d.ll                                                                                                                                           │
│ opt: llvm/lib/Transforms/Vectorize/LoopVectorize.cpp:7398: llvm::VectorizationFactor llvm::LoopVectorizationPlanner::computeBestVF(): Assertion `(BestFactor.Width == LegacyVF.Width ||                        │
│ planContainsAdditionalSimplifications(getPlanFor(BestFactor.Width), CostCtx, OrigLoop)) && " VPlan cost model and legacy cost model disagreed"' failed.                                                        │
│                                                                                                                                                                                                                │
│ ```                                                                                                                                                                                                            │
│                                                                                                                                                                                                                │
